   percent of the exact optimal profit), efficient (instant solutions for
   specific problem instances), and useful in other applications where
   mixed bundling is a subproblem. I demonstrate this by applying the
   solution to the mixed bundle problem in a vertical channel where a
   retailer must bundle and price component goods from multiple independent
   manufacturers.
